com.here.msdkui.guidance

Class GuidanceEstimatedArrivalViewData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.msdkui.guidance.GuidanceEstimatedArrivalViewData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class GuidanceEstimatedArrivalViewData
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    A data class holding information related to Estimated Arrival Time (ETA). It consists of ETA date, distance to destination and remaining travel time. Use GuidanceEstimatedArrivalViewPresenter to get notified on new instances of this class during guidance.
